   Trusted Shops API

Trusted Shops API documentation

   Integrate to the Max!

   Use our Trusted Shops APIs to get even more out of our products and
   customise them to fit your needs perfectly. Get direct access to your
   data without any detour. Some examples:
     * Manage your reviews directly in your own backend
     * Monitor your performance directly in your CRM or shop software
     * Amplify your app or build a new one
     * Show your star rating directly in the Google search results

   You can choose out of various APIs. It’s super easy. Check our APIs by
   preview, if you like. Just try it with your shop and see what you can
   do.
   Common API Advanced API
   If you want to try our advanced Trusted Shops API, please contact us to
   get your credentials.
